name: Bike helmet
description: Adult bike helmet similar to Rosebank Shakedown Helmet - Matte Black (commuter style, Australian Standards certified).

name: Bike
description: Flat-bar fitness / commuter bike such as the 2024 Marin Fairfax 1 or Specialized Sirrus 1.0, suitable for city riding (max budget about $600).

name: Nice beers
description: If you somehow find some nice imported beers (such as Estrella Damm Inedit, 1906 Black Coupage, Stiegl Goldbrau, Weihenstephaner Kristall), I would slurp them up.

name: Apfel Zimt Gluhwein
description: Sternthaler Apfel Zimt Gluhwein (Nurnberger style mulled apple wine), 1L bottle.

name: Rice cooker
description: Rice cooker with preferably a stainless steel inner pot (no Teflon), eg a 4L 316L stainless inner pot model.

name: Steam gift card
description: Steam digital gift cards range from $20-$100. Add to my pile of shame. :)

name: Flipper Zero
description: Flipper Zero is a multi-tool for pentesting, radio and access control experiments.

name: Gorgeous Geisha tea
description: Gorgeous Geisha green tea blend, loose leaf.

name: New York Breakfast
description: New York Breakfast black tea, loose leaf.

name: Shincha Green Tea
description: Shincha first harvest green tea from ITO EN Australia, about 100g pack.

name: Whisky
description: I love a nice whisky, for example Suntory Chita, Amber Lane Equinox or Starward Honeycomb.

name: Herman Miller chair
description: Second hand Herman Miller Aeron ergonomic office chair with posture fit. Armrest optional.

name: Pulsar Xlite V4
description: Pulsar Xlite V4 Medium wireless gaming mouse (white preferred but black is okay too).

name: Garmin Drive 53 GPS
description: Garmin Drive 53 AU car GPS navigator (for L and P plate driving navigation).

name: UNO No Mercy
description: UNO Show Em No Mercy Edition card game, the extra brutal house-rule style UNO variant.

name: Cascadia board game
description: Cascadia tile-laying and token-drafting board game about Pacific Northwest habitats and wildlife.

name: Wavelength
description: Wavelength social guessing party game for teams.

name: Shake Hands book
description: Shake Hands with the Devil: The Failure of Humanity in Rwanda by Romeo Dallaire.

name: Clay target voucher
description: Clay target shooting with live ammo experience voucher from RedBalloon, preferably for 2 to do with you! :)
